#To Access the Data From Another Org

Salesforce org 1:
   Connected app 
    

Salesforce org 2:
  
   auth provider
   named credential
    To get url of(org 1) : System.debug(System.Url.getSalesforceBaseUrl());
   

   
 1. we can access the data of org 1 from org 2 
    also we can manipulate the data of org1 if we have an access.
   
